text: Situated on a half acre and conveniently located a few minutes walk from Southlake Town Square, this home has it all. Mature trees line the back fence line creating a wall of privacy and seclusion that make you feel like you are on vacation year round.

text: Discover this exceptional 4-bed, 3.5-bath estate, complete with an oversized 3-car garage & BACKYARD PARADISE. A rotunda front porch welcomes you into a sprawling floorplan, drenched in natural light, and adorned with oak hardwood floors, high ceilings, plantation shutters, and designer lighting throughout. The living room features a wood-beamed ceiling, and custom floating shelves made from solid walnut and resin, plus a cozy gas fireplace with a mantle and brick accents. The open-concept living area seamlessly flows into the gourmet kitchen, equipped with top-of-the-line appliances including a built-in fridge, 6-burner gas cooktop with pot filler, double ovens, and luxurious quartz countertops. A coffee bar, along with a butlers pantry featuring a wine rack, sit nicely on either side of the walk-through pantry, adding both convenience and style. Breathtaking entry with dual staircase and three beautiful crystal chandeliers. The expansive downstairs floor plan offers multiple entertaining spaces, a primary suite and guest suite, office, and media room. The spa-like primary suite boasts dual water closets, his and her vanities, incredible walk-in shower and oversized walk in closet. First-floor offers a mother-in-law suite with private access to a covered patio with cozy fireplace. The gourmet kitchen features a Subzero refrigerator-freezer, Bertazzoni dual range, dishwasher and two trash drawers. True catering kitchen complete with additional Bertazzoni 36 in range, two ovens, microwave, second dishwasher, full size refrigerator and freezer. Between the kitchen and media is an entertainer's dream bar with 2 slider glass doors for seamless flow to the patio and pool. The upstairs layout has 2 additional ensuite bedrooms, game room and two spacious unfinished flex rooms that would make a great home gym, additional bedrooms, or a second media room. Minutes from schools, shopping, restaurants and entertainment.
